      "latin_text": "Magnus in orbe fuit \u2041\u200b rolu[tus] <...> \nEt quia morte mortem docet este tim-<...> \nFunerae sedes \u2042\u200b cavet hic partesque ma-<...> \nEtherea sedes petia bon summa pi-<...> \nVitet in eternum \u2043\u200b, quia sprevit munera v[eta], \nNesciret innumen nec viset regna proph[eta]. \nVersus Stephani.\nAnchora justicie \u2044\u200b, via fte, pons piet[atis]\nFortis perfidie destructor, lux bonit[atis],\nHugo migravit sua quem bona vita beavit.\nHinc et sanctorem grex non \u2045\u200b dolet monacorum.\nNon moritur \u2046\u200b, quoniam fruitur \u2047\u200b regno superorum \u2048\u200b\nNon igitur sapientis queritur nec turba decorum.",
